<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idc436e5e7-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87" identifier="/us/usc/t38/s8214"><num value="8214">§ 8214.</num><heading> Limitations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary may not use the authority under this subchapter to assist in the establishment of more than eight new medical schools. Such schools shall be located in geographically dispersed areas of the United States.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idc436e5e8-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/92/541/s2/a">Pub. L. 92–541, § 2(a)</ref>, <date date="1972-10-24">Oct. 24, 1972</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/86/1104">86 Stat. 1104</ref>, § 5074; renumbered § 8214, <ref href="/us/pl/102/40/tIV/s402/b/2/B">Pub. L. 102–40, title IV, § 402(b)(2)(B)</ref>, <date date="1991-05-07">May 7, 1991</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/105/239">105 Stat. 239</ref>; amended <ref href="/us/pl/102/83/s4/b/1">Pub. L. 102–83, § 4(b)(1)</ref>, (2)(E), <date date="1991-08-06">Aug. 6, 1991</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/105/404">105 Stat. 404</ref>, 405.)</sourceCredit>
